Name: Spectating Simulator The Racing
About the game: Spectating Simulator The Racing presents the opportunity to spectate car racing in first person view.Yes real close,even you can be hit by a car!There are nice built racing cars,a lot of spectators you can enjoy watching the race with.You can just enjoy spectating, or have fun going after car by running.Whole map is the place you can spectate the racing.
